{"tid":1552762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌和理非有野講，我要割蓆","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:51:23.000Z","uid":263945,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"521d678888e024321f07c20cc4e7e22d1445fd63","tid":1552762,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"首先要講明今日一直係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和平遊行</span></span><br />\n我先唔屌班死黑警set左封鎖線搞到上唔到美領<br />\n行下行下<br />\n係警察<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">首先無故地衝入中環站拉路人在先</span></span><br />\n最後搞到要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">封中環站</span></span><br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊行集會同時進行緊</span></span><br />\n同一時間警方突然要求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">45分鐘</span></span>內所有人要走晒<br />\n先唔講目測個到起碼幾十萬人，45分鐘冇可能散得晒<br />\n仲要唔好唔記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">冇耐之前先封左中環站唔比你走</span></span><br />\n好啦，當你要走啦，佢再分批運狗去中環碼頭，去金鐘銅鑼灣灣仔天后炮台山旺角太子尖沙咀黃大仙油塘地鐵站<br />\n你冇睇錯，而家黨鐵站同警署真係冇分別<br />\n屌，又要人走又封死晒，走唔到又拉人非法集結<br />\n簡單黎講佢要大圍捕，想拉你就拉你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">仆街黑警死全家</span></span><br />\n一句講晒，<br />\n今日係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警先撩起既衝突</span></span><br />\n作為和理非，我要永不割蓆"},{"pid":"e8c77de817222de7c8ea75e7afaf83e0787356d7","tid":1552762,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db74ae2b68dac74b951b7de773f6ddf421489f8e","tid":1552762,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"P牌求推，需要真相杜絕分化撚"},{"pid":"86f9bd9d5fd4c73e4c1ac24b35ab4963e95b38d5","tid":1552762,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"狗狗亂咬人，勇武法師護巿民"},{"pid":"9716eb7f7d3823e094ea8b85242b581656f5c90a","tid":1552762,"uid":34816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"屌你標題黨，唔好扮撚晒野<br />\n<br />\n#不推文回復"},{"pid":"220034e14ce8c400ab6b19653af16b273ab096a5","tid":1552762,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"知你想講乜，但你同班狗原本都唔喺同一張蓆上面，個標題有d誤導"},{"pid":"de532b2a6263a3e94cf589ed1059c891c3d7f119","tid":1552762,"uid":34020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1e9a2162632e2950c76825c2554783bef3d1d7c","tid":1552762,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">block標題黨</span>"},{"pid":"834e8d7792a85cabb15bf8d24e941cc728fb8248","tid":1552762,"uid":247640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"感謝各位前線。冇你地，我可能打唔到依段野。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553201</a>"}]}